songs.title: Keep in Touch

Unless she hella fine, then you could be mine

All I do is rap and show love at my shows
Yes, I been through a couple of hoes but they never meant shit to me though (Yuh)

It's time for you to slide, bitch I gotta ride (I gotta ride)
My homie need my help, even if I die (Even if I die)
I'mma do what I gotta do ’cause I ain't never been pie (Ain't never been pie)
I could look you in your eyes and tell that you lie
